h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click *Agent* sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Agent Currency Posting* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Agent Currency Posting"|guide:ShowExhAgentCurrencyPostingActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "Edit" button from tool bar.
* Open *Agent Currency Posting* in Edit Mode.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Select Agent Currency Posting" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get *Agent Currency Posting* details from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show selected *Agent Currency Posting* information in input form.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

